{
  "stem": "19895.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't want that anybody would feel sorry for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I talked very little, if anything, about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because I didn't want to people know me and think of me as I am some kind of a strange bird who-- who survived and went through an unbelievable scenes and misery.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I didn't want anybody to feel sorry for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I wanted to be equal, a human being who is doing the work daily, and you fit in and do well in our society.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I built my presence in daily life and a family and-- and-- enjoyed that I had a family.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I will now jump time to tell about my parents and what happened when the concentration camp for me was coming to an end.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And how, we will talk about later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I just wanted to put in a little philosophy of-- of my feelings, that even now, I don't think I want to tell about scenes of torture, and so on.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Everybody knows.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Whoever paid attention to witnesses' testimonies, that that was definitely part of it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But dehumanization, and what went in on our mind, why us, and what did we do, is something till today I cannot cope with and understand.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And please ask any questions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The Russians were coming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Russians were coming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What a-- what a-- a-- a-- an interesting statement to make.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew that the Russian front, the war efforts, were happening, and from the Eastern Front, the Russians were approaching our borders, where we were at the Austria-Hungarian border.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were dreaming of the days when they're human beings.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were talking about their families.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were talking about they wifes, which most of them were separated from.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
